flowchart LR

%% INPUTS
A[Marine Engine Exhaust CO₂] --> B[Carbon Capture Bioreactor Module]
C[Seawater Intake] --> B
D[Light Source (Solar / Artificial)] --> B

%% BIOLOGICAL CONVERSION
B --> E[Algal Biomass Suspension]
B --> F[Oxygenated Water Output]

%% CONVERSION MODULE
E --> G[Biomass Conversion Module]
G --> H[Concentrated Biomass Stream]

%% WATER RETURN
G --> I[Treated Seawater Return]
I --> J[Ocean Discharge]

%% THERMAL PROCESSING
K[Engine Waste Heat] --> L[Thermal Recovery & Conditioning Module]
H --> L
L --> M[Dry Biomass Flakes]

%% OUTPUT STREAM
M --> N[Stable Biomass Product Storage]

